msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Hm...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "This isn't a number I recognize.\r\nWho could it be...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Hello?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Ah, hi there!\r\nIt's me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Hm... Me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Yup. You know who I am."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "(I wonder who this guy is...\r\nWait, I think I recognize his voice.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "(Could it be... Daigo?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "(No. Daigo's young, but he's not <font_kind=yakuza_italic>this</font_kind> young.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "(It couldn't be Haruto, could it...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "(No, Haruto's too young to stand up\r\non his own, let alone talk on the phone.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Is that you... Taichi?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Yeah! It's me, Taichi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "I could barely tell. Do you have a cold\r\nor something? You sound kinda weird."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Yeah, this sore throat is doing a\r\nnumber on my voice!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Well, that's no good.\r\nMake sure you get some rest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "I will. By the way, are you good to talk?\r\nWhere are you right now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Hm? Oh, I'm in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Got it. Kamurocho, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Um... I know this is kinda out of the blue,\r\nbut I have something I need to ask."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Hm? What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Well, one of my friends got hurt\r\nreal bad, and it's totally my fault."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "What...!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "They're asking me to cover both\r\nthe treatment and his hospital bills."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "I don't have that kind of money, though..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "So, um... I was wondering if you'd\r\nbe able to spot me a bit of cash."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "If you can't, I'll probably end up\r\nsaddled with debt for years to come."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "(Taichi is really in trouble here...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "(Wait a second...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "(I feel like I've heard about scams\r\nthat sound a little like this.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "(I should figure out what's going on here.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Taichi, where are you calling me from?\r\nI don't recognize this number."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Oh, I got a new phone.\r\nA new number, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Wait, have you ever even owned a phone?\r\nThat's news to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Huh? Oh, s-sorry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Guess I just forgot to tell you.\r\nI actually bought one a little while ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "(Hm...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "(This is no time to be distrustful.\r\nTaichi needs my help here.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Okay, then.\r\nHow much do you need?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "They said around 200,000..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "200 grand!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Oh, but if that's too much for you,\r\nI'll take whatever you can get your hands on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "I should be able to scrounge\r\ntogether the rest myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "A-All right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "I have to wonder, though...\r\nHow did you hurt your friend so badly?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Well, uh... We got in a terrible accident."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "What? You mean, like a car accident?\r\nYou don't even have a driver's license."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Oh, uh... That's not it at all!\r\nIt was, um... more like a freak accident."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "(What is that even supposed to mean?\r\nI wonder...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Have you been wrestling again?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Uh, yeah! My friend and I were\r\npretending we were pros..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Taichi, I don't want to treat you like a kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "But that means you need to stop behaving\r\nlike one. Try to act your age, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "S-Sorry..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "And your friend?\r\nHow's he doing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "W-Well, the doctor said he'll be totally\r\nfine as long as he gets into surgery soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "So, his surgery is the top priority."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "How do you want me to send the money?\r\nI can't come back to Okinawa right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Huh? Okinawa?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Aren't you still at Morning Glory?\r\nDon't tell me... Did you leave Okinawa, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "U-Uh, oh! Th-That's right! As is the\r\ncustomary greeting in Okinawa, \"mensore\"!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "(Why would he give me an Okinawan welcome?\r\nI wonder why he's acting so strange...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "(With everything that's happened,\r\nhe's probably just looking for a distraction.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Taichi. I know things are rough right now,\r\nbut times like this are what make a man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Yeah... You're right.\r\nI've gotta get a grip here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "(With everything that's happened,\r\nhe's probably just looking for a distraction.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "(I should try to help get his mind off it.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Ah, mensore!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Wh-What? What's all that about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "...Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Anyway, I'm kinda in a hurry here.\r\nCan we get back to the point?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "I'm down in Okinawa right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "My hurt buddy's dad is apparently\r\nin Tokyo on business, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "I'm gonna need you to give him the cash."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "I'll tell him to wait over by\r\nthe Millennium Tower for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "You think you'll be able to scrape up\r\nthe money and head over there now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "...Yeah, I can do that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Great! His dad's name is Ishigaki-san,\r\njust so you know. Well, thanks again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "All right then, off to the Millennium Tower.\r\nIshigaki-san's waiting for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "(This must be someone trying to scam me.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "(I can't believe they'd really steal from\r\na random stranger over the phone.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "(I should play along and show him what\r\nhappens to people who pull stunts like this.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "All right. What do you need me to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Oh, I actually just heard my friend's dad\r\nis up in Kamurocho right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Do, um... Do you think you could\r\ngive him the money for me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Wow. That's a pretty amazing coincidence."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Isn't it? His dad's name is Ishigaki-san, by the way.\r\nI'll tell him to wait over by the Millennium Tower."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Please, can you bring him the money?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "...Yeah, I can do that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Really!? Great!\r\nWell, thanks again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "All right then, off to the Millennium Tower.\r\nI'm coming for you, you thieving bastard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "(Is this the father of the kid Taichi hurt?\r\nI'm pretty sure his name is Ishigaki.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "So, are you Ishigaki-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Ah, yes. I'm Akira Ishigaki.\r\nAnd you are?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "It's Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "Oh, so you're the guy.\r\nTaichi-kun told me everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry he's put your family\r\nthrough so much trouble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "It's okay. For now, I just want to get\r\nback to my son as soon as possible!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "Is it all right if you cover\r\nthe treatment fees, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "I don't want to put Taichi-kun in debt,\r\nbut he'll need to pay for it if you can't help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "(I need to make sure they have enough\r\nto cover their son's hospital bills.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "(More importantly, I can't let\r\nTaichi end up in debt!)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry about this. I didn't have much\r\ntime, so I couldn't get the full amount."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "I see... Okay, then. For now, I'll gladly\r\ntake whatever you have to offer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Here you are, 200 grand.\r\nPlease use this to save your son."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much.\r\nYou're a good man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "Well then, it's about time I head\r\nback to Okinawa to help my son!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Once he's out of surgery, I'll have\r\nTaichi-kun get in touch with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "I hope his son recovers soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "I should let Taichi know I gave him the money.\r\nThe number he called me from earlier should work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Hm? Damn, voicemail..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Oh well. I'll just call Morning Glory instead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Hello, Ayako? Is Taichi there?\r\nYeah, I need to talk to him for a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Taichi? I just gave Ishigaki-san the money.\r\nYou don't need to worry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "Huh? You don't know an Ishigaki?\r\nBut he's the father of the friend you hurt!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "...What? You didn't hurt any of your friends?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "By the way, your throat sounds a lot better.\r\nIt's amazing how fast you recovered."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?\r\nAre you messing with me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "No, it's just... Yeah.\r\nSorry for all the weird questions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "R-Right. Talk to you later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "(Hmm...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah. Have you seen the news on all\r\nthose phone scams that've been going around?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I feel like everyone was talking about them.\r\nThe ones where they pretend to be someone you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "I dunno, but wouldn't their voice be different?\r\nWho'd fall for something like that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "For real. Anyone dumb enough to get suckered\r\nin by something like that practically deserves it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Let's get out of here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "R-Right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "Dammit. That lesson came at a price."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "(Something seems wrong about this.\r\nIt has to be a scam...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "(I should try to catch him in his lie.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "Hold on.\r\nCan I actually ask you something first?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "S-Sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "(This must be the guy that fake Taichi told me about.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "So, are you Ishigaki-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "Ah, yes. I'm Akira Ishigaki. And you are?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "The name's Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "Oh, so you're the guy.\r\nTaichi-kun told me everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "Anyway, about those treatment fees..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "Actually, can I ask you something first?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "S-Sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "You've... spent some time with\r\nTaichi before, haven't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "Yes, of course."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "Then, you know about the huge burn scar\r\nhe has across the side of his face, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "Has he ever mentioned how it happened?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "No, he's never brought it up.\r\nIt seemed best not to mention it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "(Got him.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san? Is something wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "Not at all. I just didn't think you'd\r\ngive yourself away so easily. Thanks for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "...Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "If you knew Taichi, you'd know\r\nhe doesn't have a scar at all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "Wh-What!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "I wasn't expecting it to be that easy.\r\nYou thieves aren't the brightest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "You fucking prick. I guess I don't have a choice\r\nnow that you caught me. Hey, c'mon out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "Man, this old fart figured us out?\r\nWhat a pain in the ass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "You... You're the one from the phone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "It's me, Taichi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "Heh, guess we're gonna have to do this the hard way.\r\nTime to beat the cash outta you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Hey, gramps! You're finished!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "P-Please, we've had enough!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "You better swear... you'll never try to pull\r\nanother one of these ridiculous scams again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "O-Okay! We promise, we promise!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "R-Run away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "Hello?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "Ah, hi there!\r\nIt's me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "Me...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "Yeah! It's me, Taichi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "It hasn't even been 30 seconds, you little punk.\r\nDo you need me to teach you another lesson!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "U-Uncle Kaz, is something wrong?\r\nYou're scaring me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "Wait, is this really Taichi?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "I mean, I said it was Taichi, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "I was just calling to say hello.\r\nSorry, are you too busy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "O-Oh. No, it's okay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "Phew. I'm glad I got to hear your voice,\r\nUncle Kaz. Anyway, talk to you later!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "Right. Say hi to the others for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "Scams are everywhere... I've gotta check\r\nwho's on the other end when I answer."
msgstr ""

